      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1353958-the-stranger-beside-me">Quotes from The Stranger Besi...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;As I write these recollections of women who survived, I hope my readers are taking careful note of why they did.<br />They screamed.<br />They fought.<br />They slammed doors in a stranger's face.<br />They ran.<br />They doubted glib stories.<br />They spotted flaws in those stories.<br />They were lucky enough to have someone step up and protect them.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/9337151-as-i-write-these-recollections-of-women-who-survived-i">15 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
